20in%20the%20fallout%20of%20Winn%20stealing%20around%20%C2%A364%2C000%20(%2486%2C393)%20while%20working%20as%20a%20bookkeeper%20in%20the%20mid-2000s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERos%20Hemmings%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Winns'%20real%20names%20are%20Sally%20and%20Tim%20Walker.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinn%20was%20questioned%20but%20never%20charged%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20embezzlement%2C%20and%20she%20and%20her%20former%20employer%20settled%20the%20disagreement%20privately.%20Winn%20confirmed%20these%20details%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Wednesday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20so%2C%20the%20couple%20borrowed%20%C2%A3100%2C000%20from%20a%20family%20friend.%20When%20that%20friend%20faced%20financial%20trouble%20of%20his%20own%2C%20debt%20collectors%20recouped%20the%20loan%20by%20taking%20the%20Winns'%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Observer%20also%20cast%20doubt%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20Moth's%20illness%2C%20reporting%20that%20it%20spoke%20to%20medical%20experts%20who%20were%20skeptical%20that%20he%20had%20CBD.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fconditions%2Fcorticobasal-degeneration%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENHS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20average%20life%20expectancy%20of%20someone%20with%20CBD%20is%20around%20six%20to%20eight%20years%20from%20when%20their%20symptoms%20start.%20Winn%20has%20said%20Moth%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20the%20condition%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCqOKYVZI9Km%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%2012%20years%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20found%20evidence%20that%20the%20Winns%20owned%20a%20property%20in%20France%20in%202013%2C%20meaning%20that%20they%20were%20not%20homeless%20when%20they%20began%20their%20journey%20as%20described%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Salt%20Path.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223bb35ab7-4a87-43df-aa05-03968f105b34%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaynor%20Winn%20denied%20parts%20of%20The%20Observer%20report%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225851%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%26quot%3BThe%20Salt%20Path%26quot%3B%20author%20Raynor%20Winn%20and%20her%20husband%20Moth%20Winn%2C%20whose%20real%20names%20are%20Sally%20Walker%20and%20Tim%20Walker.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687266c685e81483682deb6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223784%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Salt%20Path%26quot%3B%20author%20Raynor%20Winn%20and%20her%20husband%20Moth%20Winn%2C%20whose%20real%20names%20are%20Sally%20Walker%20and%20Tim%20Walker.%3Cp%3EHugh%20R%20Hastings%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Winn%20shared%20a%20length%20statement%20on%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.raynorwinn.co.uk%2Fnew-page%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20allegations%20of%20embezzlement%2C%20she%20stated%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bwas%20a%20pressured%20time%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20years%20before%20the%202008%20economic%20crisis.%20%26quot%3BAny%20mistakes%20I%20made%20during%20the%20years%20in%20that%20office%2C%20I%20deeply%20regret%2C%20and%20I%20am%20truly%20sorry%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20maintained%20that%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20lost%20their%20house%20after%20investing%20in%20a%20lifelong%20friend's%20property%20portfolio%2C%20which%20left%20the%20couple%20liable%20for%20large%20sums%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20house%20in%20France%2C%20Winn%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20uninhabitable%20ruin%20in%20a%20bramble%20patch.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20attempted%20to%20sell%20it%20in%202013%2C%20but%20were%20told%20by%20a%20local%20estate%20agent%20that%20there%20was%20no%20point%20marketing%20it%20as%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bvirtually%20worthless.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinn%20also%20shared%20photos%20of%20documents%20appearing%20to%20confirm%20her%20husband's%20diagnosis%2C%20one%20of%20which%20showed%20that%20he%20had%20previously%20been%20considered%20as%20having%20an%20%26quot%3Batypical%26quot%3B%20CBD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinn%20wrote%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Bwill%20always%20be%20grateful%20that%20Moth's%20version%20of%20CBS%20is%20indolent%2C%20its%20slow%20progression%20has%20allowed%20us%20time%20to%20discover%20how%20walking%20helps%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20charity%20PSPA%2C%20which%20supports%20people%20with%20CBD%20and%20progressive%20supranuclear%20palsy%2C%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pspassociation.org.uk%2Fnews%2Fpspas-response-to-the-observer-article%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMonday%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bshocked%20and%20disappointed%20to%20learn%20of%20the%20allegations%26quot%3B%20and%20had%20cut%20ties%20with%20them.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fallout%2C%20Winn%20has%20also%20withdrawn%20from%20a%20planned%2017-stop%20tour%20of%20the%20UK%2C%20which%20would%20have%20seen%20her%20perform%20readings%20alongside%20a%20band.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d643253-b277-4cc5-9745-cd573f79b76a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20an%20author%20has%20come%20under%20fire%20for%20lying%20to%20readers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20scandals%20in%20the%20past%20surrounding%20books%20marketed%20as%20memoirs%20that%20have%20later%20been%20found%20out%20to%20part%20or%20wholly%20falsified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20The%20Smoking%20Gun%20website%20reported%20that%20large%20parts%20of%20James%20Frey's%202003%20memoir%20about%20his%20struggles%20with%20drug%20and%20alcohol%20addiction%20and%20subsequent%20recovery%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20Million%20Little%20Pieces%2C%26quot%3B%20were%20exaggerated%20or%20fabricated.%20Readers%20who%20felt%20misled%20filed%20lawsuits%20against%20both%20Frey%20and%20his%20publisher%2C%20Random%20House%2C%20th