0a%20space%20I%20had%20been%20searching%20for.%20The%20experience%20was%20full%20of%20insight%20on%20sustainable%20practices%20and%20the%20people%20were%20curious%2C%20kind%2C%20and%20had%20similar%20thought%20processes%2C%20thus%20making%20it%20even%20more%20special.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20memorable%20moments%20for%20me%20was%20learning%20about%20how%20roots%20connect%20underground%20and%20how%20soil%20functions%20much%20like%20the%20human%20body.%20As%20someone%20trained%20in%20homoeopathy%2C%20that%20parallel%20was%20incredibly%20exciting.%20And%20yes%2C%20I%20dug%20my%20hands%20into%20cow%20dung%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%20absolutely%20loved%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20impactful%20moments%20during%20the%20workshop%20was%20a%20life%20cycle%20analysis%20(LCA)%20activity%2C%20which%20revealed%20the%20hidden%20environmental%20cost%20of%20everyday%20consumer%20habits.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20really%20hit%20me%2C%20I%20uninstalled%20all%20my%20e-commerce%20apps%20while%20still%20on%20the%20farm%2C%20and%20have%20not%20felt%20the%20urge%20to%20go%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGoodbye%20apps%2C%20hello%20conscious%20living%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20workshop%2C%20Srushti%20has%20begun%20planning%20a%20green%20space%20of%20her%20own%2C%20with%20native%20trees%2C%20birds%2C%20and%20a%20small%20food-growing%20area.%20A%20chance%20connection%20with%20a%20native%20plant%20expert%20at%20the%20farm%20helped%20her%20finally%20convince%20her%20parents%20that%20native%20plants%20can%20be%20beautiful%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShamika%20Bhide%2C%20a%2031-year-old%20playback%20singer%20based%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20attended%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F424318%2Ffive-farm-volunteering-opportunities-in-tamil-nadu-auroville-chennai-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epermaculture%20wor