st-likely-the-oldest-comet-ever-seen-say-researchers-13395445%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Indian%20Heroes%20Who%20Became%20Legends%20in%20Wildlife%20Conservation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20wildlife%20conservation%20in%20India%20is%20not%20just%20about%20battling%20an%20overbearing%2C%20cruel%20and%20amoral%20system%20of%20governance%20but%20also%20about%20overcoming%20ignorance%20and%20public%20apathy.%20That%20is%20why%20on%20World%20Animal%20Welfare%20Day%2C%20it%20feels%20pertinent%20to%20highlight%20the%20contributions%20of%20certain%20individuals%20in%20our%20past%20who%20not%20only%20challenged%20the%20status%20quo%20but%20also%20raised%20public%20consciousness%20and%20inspired%20action%20against%20the%20incredible%20cruelty%20met%20to%20our%20precious%20wildlife.%20To%20keep%20alive%20the%20memory%20of%20their%20work%20is%20to%20remember%20what%20it%20means%20to%20preserve%20our%20wildlife.%C2%A0%3Cem%3E(Above%20images%20of%20Kailash%20Sankhala%2C%20J%20Vijaya%20%26amp%3B%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%3A%20What%20it%20means%20to%20co-exist%20with%20snow%20leopards%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20having%20a%20famous%20father%20in%20Colonel%20Chewang%20Rinchen%2C%20a%20decorated%20Ladakhi%20soldier%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246169%2Fladakh-snow-leopard-conservancy-india-trust-saviours-rinchen-wangchuk-tsewang-namgail-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERinchen%20Wangchuk%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0forged%20his%20own%20path.%20As%20a%20wildlife%20researcher%20from%20Ladakh%2C%20he%20framed%20a%20question%20that%20would%20address%20the%20fundamental%20challenge%20of%20snow%20leopard%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20reconcile%20the%20notion%20of%20snow%20leopard%20conservation%20with%20the%20needs%20of%20lo