0also%20enhances%20their%20yield%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrafting%20costs%20around%20Rs%20100%20per%20sapling%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20Parmeshwar%20grafted%20around%20250%20new%20saplings.%20These%20plants%20are%20expected%20to%20start%20fruiting%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%20%E2%80%9CGrafting%20is%20a%20game-changer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20extends%20the%20lifespan%20of%20avocado%20plants%20and%20boosts%20their%20yield%20potential.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%2C%20a%2062-year-old%20retired%20postal%20employee%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20supporting%20Parmeshwar%20by%20supplying%20avocado%20plants%20for%20his%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20I%20come%20from%20a%20non-farming%20background%2C%20we%20both%20began%20this%20journey%20of%20avocado%20farming%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Parmeshwar%20visited%20Karnataka%20to%20learn%20about%20avocado%20cultivation%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20speak%20Kannada%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20we%20met.%20I%20explained%20everything%20to%20him.%20His%20perseverance%20and%20dedication%20were%20clear%2C%20and%20over%20time%2C%20they%20helped%20him%20become%20a%20successful%20avocado%20farmer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20avocado%20saplings%20I%20planted%20have%20yet%20to%20bear%20fruit.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Parmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20farm%20is%20thriving%2C%20and%20he%E2%80%99s%20now%20successfully%20harvesting%20avocados!%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeading%20by%20example%3A%20Educating%20the%20next%20generation%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20journey%20into%20avocado%20farming%20is%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336695%2Finnovations-by-farmers-indian-agriculture-solar-dryer-biofertiliser-tree-scooter-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C