0lifted%20off%2C%20I%20could%20feel%20my%20whole%20life%20changing%20in%20a%20moment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Poonam%E2%80%99s%20hard%20work%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20always%20welcomed%20with%20clear%20skies.%20There%20were%20moments%20of%20doubt%20and%20exhaustion%2C%20and%20of%20questioning%20her%20ability%20and%20choices.%20%E2%80%9CAviation%20training%20is%20intense.%20Balancing%20it%20with%20studies%20and%20family%20responsibilities%20was%20indeed%20difficult%2C%20but%20I%20never%20gave%20up.%20I%20kept%20thinking%20about%20my%20brother.%20If%20he%20could%20face%20life%20with%20such%20courage%2C%20so%20could%20I.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20mindset%20helped%20her%20again%20and%20again%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20the%20cockpit%2C%20where%20every%20second%20counted.%20Among%20those%20moments%2C%20one%20during%20her%20time%20at%20Jet%20Airways%20has%20stayed%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-66-1752129541.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Now%20working%20as%20a%20Flight%20Operations%20Inspector%20with%20the%20DGCA%2C%20Poonam%20helps%20keep%20flight%20operations%20across%20the%20country%20safe%20and%20accountable.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-66-1752129541.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-66-1752129541-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-66-1752129541-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-66-1752129541-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-66-175