C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20work%20now%20is%20about%20setting%20and%20maintaining%20the%20highest%20safety%20standards%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20audit%2C%20every%20training%20review%20%E2%80%94%20it%20all%20comes%20down%20to%20one%20thing%3A%20keeping%20our%20skies%20safe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInside%20a%20pilot%E2%80%99s%20mind%20during%20a%20mid-air%20emergency%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20safety%20concerns%20have%20been%20a%20recent%20topic%20of%20discussion%20in%20the%20aviation%20industry%2C%20Poonam%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20pilots%20around%20the%20globe%20are%20trained%20to%20face%20all%20the%20possible%20technical%20dangers%20that%20can%20be%20imagined.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20six%20months%2C%20pilots%20undergo%20training%20in%20a%20simulated%20setup.%20The%20process%20is%20divided%20into%20two%20days.%20On%20the%20first%20day%2C%20we%20have%20a%20four-hour%20session%2C%20and%20on%20the%20second%2C%20we%20go%20for%20checks.%20One%20of%20the%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20during%20emergencies%20for%20pilots%20is%20to%20%3Cem%3Eaviate%2C%20navigate%2C%20and%20communicate%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Poonam%20says.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98Aviate%E2%80%99%20means%20that%20we%20need%20to%20fly%20the%20aircraft%2C%20%E2%80%98navigate%E2%80%99%20is%20about%20knowing%20where%20you%20are%20going%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98communicate%E2%80%99%20means%20staying%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20Air%20Traffic%20Controller%20(ATC).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20explains%20that%20pilots%20are%20trained%20to%20handle%20all%20kinds%20of%20emergencies%20%E2%80%94%20from%20engine%20failures%20and%20fires%20to%20rapid%20decompression%2C%20which%20happens%20when%20the%20cabin%20suddenly%20loses%20pressure.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20train%20for%20these%20situations%20regularly%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CEven%